      "content": "thanks for the tip about the steam and the temperature. i feel like there's almost a sense of \"magic\" when you see it go from a pale dough to that perfect golden color in the oven. is there anything else that can mess it up? like what makes a crust look uneven or blotchy instead of that nice even brown?",
